com.google.gwt.dev.jjs
Class SourceOrigin

java.lang.Object
  com.google.gwt.dev.jjs.SourceOrigin
All Implemented Interfaces:
SourceInfo, java.io.Serializable
public class SourceOrigin
extends java.lang.Object
implements SourceInfo

Describes where a SourceInfo's node came from. This class currently includes only physical origin information, but could be extended to provide support for source-Module and -Generators. TODO: rename this class to make it parallel to SourceInfoCorrelation? TODO: make this package-protected?
